node.text:
Check out these delicate micro tattoos! 🎨🖊️

🔹 Mystical Eye Tattoo 👁️ – Placed just behind the ear, this fine line design with dotwork details symbolizes intuition, protection, and inner wisdom. A subtle but powerful statement piece!

🔹 Angel Wings Tattoo 👼 – A tiny yet meaningful forearm tattoo featuring angel wings and a halo, representing guidance, remembrance, and spiritual protection.

🔹 Lucky Four-Leaf Clover Tattoo 🍀 – This minimalist clover on the wrist is a timeless symbol of good luck and fortune, drawn with delicate linework to keep it light and elegant.

Which one is your favorite? Let me know in the comments! 💬👇
